text: Hohlbach may refer to: * Hohlbach (Nidda), a river of Hesse, Germany, tributary of the Nidda * Hohlbach (Haidenaab), a river of Bavaria, Germany, tributary of the Haidenaab * Hohlbach, a former subdivision of the municipality Hollenegg, Deutschlandsberg District, Styria, Austria
title: Hohlbach
